public void visit(int version,

when this method is called MethodCriteria.isMatch(className) is checked to see if any injection is necessary. If not, then the default visitor is set to bypass the injection process.

when this method is called MethodCriteria.isMatch(className, methodName, ...) is checked to see if any injection is necessary for this method. If not, then the bypass visitor is used. Otherwise, the default visitor is used (which was set in the class visit method).
